G1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB4545e3de" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
  Little League sponsorship</a>) that create the long-term relationships.</=
li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Theory 1, I have said, is the standard theory =
of modern capital markets; Theory 2 is the traditional theory of=C2=A0<em>b=
anking</em>. Theory 2 more or less describes how most banks mostly work; Th=
eory 1 more or less describes why <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/32995076.257419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9=
uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMTAvc3RhcnR1cC1iYW5rLWhhZC1hLXN0YXJ0dXAtYmFuay1ydW=
