lid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked</a>, several <a href=3D"https://link=
.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32995076.257419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZ=
XJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTAtMDQvc2JmLXdhcy1yZWNrbGVzcy1mcm9t=
LXRoZS1zdGFydD9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMDExMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV=
